  <p>This is an educational breakdown of TB-4 covering its mechanisms, clinical research, dosing protocols, and safety profile. It is <strong>not a recommendation to use TB-4</strong>. TB-4 is not FDA-approved for medical use. Consult a qualified healthcare provider before considering any peptide regimen.</p>
