<p>TB-4 has been studied across a wide range of injury types. Here's what the preclinical and early clinical data actually shows.</p>

<h3>Wound Healing</h3>

<p>This is TB-4's most extensively studied application. Multiple animal models show significant acceleration of wound closure, with improved tissue quality compared to controls.</p>

